<i>noun</i>: 찰과상 [찰과상], 연마 [연ː마], 마모 [마모] <br>
<ul><li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>찰과상 [찰과상]</dt><br>
<dd>abrasion; scratch</dd><br>
<dd>무엇에 긁히거나 쓸려서 생긴 상처.</dd><br>
<dd>A wound from scratching or scraping against something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>연마 [연ː마]</dt><br>
<dd>1. grinding; polishing; abrasion</dd><br>
<dd>금속이나 돌 등을 갈고 닦아 표면을 반질반질하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of grinding and polishing a metal, rock, etc., and smoothening the surface.</dd><br>
<dd>2. study; training; practice</dd><br>
<dd>몸, 마음, 지식, 기술 등을 힘써 다스리거나 익힘.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of disciplining one's body and mind or acquiring knowledge, skills, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>마모 [마모]</dt><br>
<dd>wear and tear; abrasion</dd><br>
<dd>마찰이 일어난 부분이 닳아서 작아지거나 없어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a part of something gets smaller or worn out after being repeatedly rubbed against something else.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>